This lab uses the [Olaf Hartong Sysmon Modular Configuration](https://github.com/olafhartong/sysmon-modular).

Source

- Repository: https://github.com/olafhartong/sysmon-modular
- Direct config file used: [sysmonconfig.xml](https://raw.githubusercontent.com/olafhartong/sysmon-modular/master/sysmonconfig.xml)

This config enables high-fidelity Windows telemetry for:

- Process creation and termination (Event ID 1, 5)
- Network connections (Event ID 3)
- Registry tampering (Event ID 13)
- DLL image loads (Event ID 7)
- Driver loads (Event ID 6)
- DNS queries (Event ID 22)
- File creation (Event ID 11)
- WMI events (Event ID 21)

It also supports MITRE ATT&CK tagging for detection engineering.

Modifications

None yet. Future labs may include stripped-down configs for specific use cases (e.g., network-only or process-only).

